#!/bin/sh
set -eu

cat <<'MSG'
Allowed commands:
  aws
  terraform
  tf-init
  tf-apply
  ansible
  ansible-playbook
  ansible-run
  ansible-destroy
  pulumi
  pulumi-python
  vim
  make
  clear
  mkdir
  rm
  chmod
  sleep
  ls
  cat
  pwd
  whoami
  id

Notes:
- Login shell allows `cd` within `/workspace` so you can move into `terraform/`, `ansible/`, and `pulumi/python`.
- Terraform and Pulumi providers are bundled for offline use.
- Use `vim` to edit files inside `/workspace`.
MSG
